ernal-examination"><span class="hover-flip-item"><span data-text="Internal Examination">Internal Examination</span></span></a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="col-lg-12 col-xxl-12 single-mega-item d-none d-md-block"><div class="custom-ads-wrapper" style="text-align: justify;"><hr class="m-0 my-md-3"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Our UG and PG courses are designed to equip students with the knowledge, skills, and competencies needed to succeed in their chosen fields and contribute positively to society. Through rigorous academic training, hands-on experience, and industry partnerships, we strive to empower our students to become future leaders, innovators, and change-makers. Join us at Sir Syed Institute for Technical Studies and embark on a journey of academic excellence and personal growth....</span></div></div></div></div></div></li><li class="with-megamenu has-menu-child-item position-static"><a class="" href="https://sirsyedinstitute.ac.in/about-us/college#">Departments<i class="feather-chevron-down"></i></a><div class="custom-megamenu grid-item-3 "><div class="wrapper shadow"><div class="row row--15"><div class="col-lg-12 col-xxl-12 single-mega-item d-none d-md-block"><div class="custom-ads-wrapper" style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Welcome to the Sir Syed Institute for Technical Studies, where we foster innovation, critical thinking, and academic excellence across a diverse range of disciplines. Our institute is dedicated to providing top-tier education and practical skills development in various fields.</span></div></div><div class="col-lg-12"><div class="row justify-content-center"><hr class="my-3"><div class="col-lg-12 col-xl-4 col-xxl-4 single-mega-item"><ul class="mega-menu-item"><li><a href="https://sirsyedinstitute.ac.in/departments/biochemistry"><span class="hover-flip-item"><span data-text="Biochemistry">Biochemistry</span></span></a></li><li><a href="https://sirsyedinstitute.ac.in/departments/bba"><span class="hover-