dinstitute.ac.in/about-us/college#">Campus Life<i class="feather-chevron-down"></i></a><div class="custom-megamenu grid-item-3 "><div class="wrapper shadow"><div class="row row--15"><div class="col-lg-12 col-xl-4 col-xxl-4 single-mega-item d-none d-md-block"><div class="custom-ads-wrapper shadow"><div class="d-block" href="#"><img alt="Education Images" loading="lazy" width="200" height="250" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" srcset="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fsirsyedinstitute.ac.in%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Fmenu%2Fcollegemain.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fsirsyedinstitute.ac.in%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Fmenu%2Fcollegemain.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 2x" src="./colg_files/collegemain.jpeg" style="color: transparent; object-fit: cover;"></div></div></div><div class="col-lg-12 col-xl-4 col-xxl-4 single-mega-item"><h3 class="custom-short-title d-none d-md-block">Library</h3><div class="custom-ads-wrapper d-none d-md-block" style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Sir Syed Institute for Technical Studies Library&nbsp;is working with a vision and mission of “Connecting people with information and empowering them with knowledge”.</span></div><ul class="mega-menu-item"><li><a href="https://sirsyedinstitute.ac.in/campus-life/library"><span>Library</span></a></li><li><a href="https://sirsyedinstitute.ac.in/about-us/college#"><span>Digital Library</span></a></li></ul></div><div class="col-lg-12 col-xl-3 col-xxl-3 single-mega-item"><h3 class="custom-short-title">Know More</h3><ul class="mega-menu-item"><li><a href="https://sirsyedinstitute.ac.in/campus-life/facilities"><span>Facilities</span></a></li><li><a href="https://sirsyedinstitute.ac.in/gallery"><span>Image Gallery</span></a></li><li><a href="https://sirsyedinstitute.ac.in/campus-life/video-gallery"><span>Video Gallery</span></a></li><li><a target="_blank" href="https://onlinetcsssits.meshilogic.co.in/Login.aspx"><span>College Portal</span></a></li><li><a href="https://sirsyedinstitute.ac.