\"SEMINAR HALL\",\"date\":\"2025-01-13T04:30:00.000Z\",\"images\":[{\"fileCaption\":\"b\",\"filePath\":\"uploads/biotech summit3-2025-04-08-15-58-14.944.jpeg\"}],\"dateFrom\":null,\"dateTo\":null},{\"_id\":\"67e56f8fef18486673b3cb83\",\"menuName\":\"News\",\"title\":\"The College Kalotsavam 'Tharang' 2025\",\"excerpt\":\"The College Kalotsavam 'Tharang' was held at Sir Syed Institute for Technical Studies from 6th to 8th January 2025. The event was organized by the College Union in connection with the University Kalotsavam. The ...\",\"location\":\"auditorium\",\"date\":\"2025-01-06T04:30:00.000Z\",\"images\":[{\"fileCaption\":\"t1\",\"filePath\":\"uploads/tharang2-2025-03-27-15-37-46.895.jpeg\"}],\"dateFrom\":null,\"dateTo\":null},{\"_id\":\"67e56f12ef18486673b3cb43\",\"menuName\":\"News\",\"title\":\"Distribution of PTA Merit Scholarship Awards and LCD Projectors\",\"excerpt\":\"The Distribution of PTA Merit Scholarship Awards and LCD Projectors ceremony was held on 1st January 2025 at the Seminar Hall. The event was a significant occasion for recognizing academic excellence and providing ...\",\"location\":\"NEW SEMINAR HALL\",\"date\":\"2025-01-01T08:30:00.000Z\",\"images\":[{\"fileCaption\":\"p3\",\"filePath\":\"uploads/pta merit1-2025-03-27-15-31-13.411.jpeg\"}],\"dateFrom\":null,\"dateTo\":null},{\"_id\":\"67e56e90ef18486673b3cb13\",\"menuName\":\"News\",\"title\":\"BIO DIVERSITY CLUB INAUGURATION\",\"excerpt\":\"The inauguration of BIO DIVERSITY CLUB was held on 01.01.2025 at the new seminar hall.The event was inaugurated by Dr.P Sreeja,HOD,Department of PG studies and research in Botany ,SIRSYED College and TSG Member,Kerala ...\",\"location\":\"NEW SEMINAR HALL\",\"date\":\"2025-01-01T04:30:00.000Z\",\"images\":[{\"fileCaption\":\"b4\",\"filePath\":\"uploads/biodiversity3-2025-03-27-15-28-51.155.jpeg\"}]}],\"whysirsyed\":[{\"_id\":\"667fbcbaccc2f92f2555a419\",\"menuName\":\"why sirsyed\",\"title\":\"ACADEMIC EXCELLENCE\",\"excerpt\":\"Sir Syed Institute for Technical Studies offers the best academic platforms for a student to excel. It culminates in a diverse student body and inclusive policies contributing to a broader learning experience, fostering ...\",\"images\":[{\"fileCaption\":\"Academic Excellence\",\"filePath\":\"uploads/WhatsApp Image 2023-07-15 at 16.36.55-2025-05-04-16-38-02.971.jpeg\"}],\"files\":[],\"links\":[],\"description\":\"\u003cp dir=\\\"ltr\\\"\u003eSir Syed Institute for Technical Studies offers the best academic platforms for a student to excel. It culminates in a diverse student body and inclusive policies contributing to a broader learning experience, fostering a more comprehensive understanding of different perspectives and ideas. Accreditation from respected educational bodies and recognition for specific programs or departments affirm the college\u0026rsquo;s commitment to academic standards. SSITS believes in providing academic advising, tutoring, counselling, and other support services that play a vital role in student success and academic achievement.\u003c/p\u003e\\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\",\"date\":null,\"order\":1},{\"_id\":\"667fbccfccc2f92f2555a41f\",\"menuName\":\"why sirsyed\",\"title\":\"BEST FACULTY TO MENTOR YOU\",\"excerpt\":\"Expertise, qualifications, and teaching methods of our professors significantly increases the learning experience. Highly skilled and dedicated faculty members contribute to academic excellence. We at SSITS encourage ...\",\"order\":2,\"images\":[{\"fileCaption\":\"Best Faculty\",\"filePath\":\"uploads/pexels-element5-1370298-2024-07-02-06-35-33.464.jpg\"}],\"files\":[],\"links\":[],\"description\":\"\u003cp dir=\\\"ltr\\\"\u003eExpertise, qualifications, and teaching methods of our professors significantly increases the learning experience. Highly skilled and dedicated faculty members contribute to academic excellence. We at SSITS encourage innovative teaching methods, incorporating new technologies, and adapting swiftly to the evolving educational needs to excel academically.\u003c/p\u003e\\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\"},{\"_id\":\"667fbcf0ccc2f92f2555a429\",\"menuName\":\"why sirsyed\",\"title\":\"HOLISTIC DEVELOPMENT\",\"excerpt\":\"We offer a curriculum that integrates various subjects, encourages critical thinking, creativity, and problem-solving skills, and includes arts, sports, and extracurricular activities. Providing support services like ...\",\"order\":3,\"images\":[{\"fileCaption\":\"Holistic Development\",\"filePath\":\"uploads/pexels-polina-tankilevitch-3735709-2024-07-02-06-36-32.696.jpg\"}],\"files\":[],\"links\":[],\"description\":\"\u003cp dir=\\\"ltr\\\"\u003eWe offer a curriculum that integrates various subjects, encourages critical thinking, creativity, and problem-solving skills, and includes arts, sports, and extracurricular activities. Providing support services like counselling, mentorship programs, and workshops helps our students manage stress, build resilience, and develop emotional intelligence. At SSITS we provide students with ample opportunities for discussions, ethical education, and exposure to diverse perspectives to develop a strong ethical compass and a sense of social responsibility.\u003c/p\u003e\\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\"},{\"_id\":\"667fbd09ccc2f92f2555a42d\",\"menuName\":\"why sirsyed\",\"title\":\"INTERACTIVE LEARNING\",\"excerpt\":\"Incorporating diverse teaching strategies such as group discussions, debates, problem-solving activities, role-playing, and hands-on experiments to cater to different learning styles, we use educational technology tools, ...\",\"order\":4,\"images\":[{\"fileCaption\":\"Interactive Learning\",\"filePath\":\"uploads/pexels-cottonbro-6208929-2024-07-02-06-37-10.155.jpg\"}],\"files\":[],\"links\":[],\"description\":\"\u003cp\u003eIncorporating diverse teaching strategies such as group discussions, debates, problem-solving activities, role-playing, and hands-on experiments to cater to different learning styles, we use educational technology tools, interactive apps, multimedia resources, and online platforms to enhance engagement and provide interactive learning experiences. Therefore, fostering a collaborative atmosphere where students work together on projects, share ideas, and learn from each other's perspectives. We also encourage and value student participation by asking open-ended questions, inviting opinions, and allowing students to contribute to discussions.\u003c/p\u003e\\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\"},{\"_id\":\"667fbd22ccc2f92f2555a432\",\"menuName\":\"why sirsyed\",\"title\":\"BETTER TOMORROW\",\"excerpt\":\"Encouraging our students towards global awareness, cultural understanding, and empathy in education fosters a sense of global citizenship that makes them capable of addressing global challenges collaboratively. Also ...\",\"order\":5,\"images\":[{\"fileCaption\":\"Better Tomorrow\",\"filePath\":\"uploads/pexels-pixabay-267885-2024-07-02-06-38-02.679.jpg\"}],\"files\":[],\"links\":[],\"description\":\"\u003cp\u003eEncouraging our students towards global awareness, cultural understanding, and empathy in education fosters a sense of global citizenship that makes them capable of addressing global challenges collaboratively. Also encouraging collaboration and community engagement in education fosters a sense of responsibility towards society, promoting active participation in creating a better future for all. Embracing innovation and technology in education at SSITS, prepares our students for the evolving industries and equips them with essential digital skills necessary for the future workforce.\u003c/p\u003e\\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\"}],\"programmes\":[{\"_id\":\"6831f54b22d8d5e6096d15c4\",\"menuName\":\"Achievement\",\"title\":\"B.Sc Biotechnology Rank Holders 2025\",\"excerpt\":\"Ms. Jomol Joy and Ms. Devendu K.V, Final year B.Sc Biotechnology students bagged I and III ranks in the Kannur University\u0026nbsp; B.Sc Biotechnology Degree Examination\u0026nbsp; 2025. Congratulations\",\"date\":\"2025-05-20T18:30:00.000Z\",\"images\":[{\"fileCaption\":\"BSc Biotechnology Rank Holders 2025\",\"filePath\":\"uploads/WhatsApp Image 2025-05-20 at 12.09.23 PM-2025-05-24-16-41-42.373.jpeg\"}],\"files\":[],\"links\":[],\"description\":\"\u003cp\u003eMs. Jomol Joy and Ms. Devendu K.V, Final year B.Sc Biotechnology students bagged I and III ranks in the Kannur University\u0026nbsp; B.Sc Biotechnology Degree Examination\u0026nbsp; 2025. Congratulations\u003c/p\u003e\"},{\"_id\":\"6831f60022d8d5e6096d15f2\",\"menuName\":\"Achievement\",\"title\":\"Rank Holders B.Sc Biochemistry Degree Examination 2025\",\"excerpt\":\"Ms. Fathima Nasli A, Final year B.Sc Biochemistry student bagged\u0026nbsp; II rank in the Kannur University\u0026nbsp; B.Sc Biochemistry Degree Examination\u0026nbsp; 2025. Congratulations\",\"date\":\"2025-05-19T18:30:00.000Z\",\"images\":[{\"fileCaption\":\"BSc Biochemistry Rank Holders 2025\",\"filePath\":\"uploads/WhatsApp Image 2025-05-24 at 9.57.58 PM-2025-05-24-16-42-28.173.jpeg\"}],\"files\":[],\"links\":[],\"description\":\"\u003cp\u003eMs. Fathima Nasli A, Final year B.Sc Biochemistry student bagged\u0026nbsp; II rank in the Kannur University\u0026nbsp; B.Sc Biochemistry Degree Examination\u0026nbsp; 2025. Congratulations\u003c/p\u003e\"},{\"_id\":\"6831f69c22d8d5e6096d1630\",\"menuName\":\"Achievement\",\"title\":\"Rank Holders B.Sc Microbiology Degree Examination 2025\",\"excerpt\":\"Ms. Geethika Rajesh and Ms. Fathima V.K, Final year B.Sc Microbiology students bagged I and II ranks in the Kannur University\u0026nbsp; B.Sc Microbiology Degree Examination\u0026nbsp; 2025. Congratulations\",\"date\":\"2025-05-18T18:30:00.000Z\",\"images\":[{\"fileCaption\":\"B.Sc Microbiology Rank Holders 2025\",\"filePath\":\"uploads/WhatsApp Image 2025-05-20 at 2.36.43 PM-2025-05-24-16-43-12.973.jpeg\"}],\"files\":[],\"links\":[],\"description\":\"\u003cp\u003eMs. Geethika Rajesh and Ms